  <datafield tag="999" ind1="C" ind2="5">
    <subfield code="m">It is worth emphasizing that there are several ways to define the effective size of a black-hole system. In particular, the black-hole spacetime is characterized by an infinite throat in the extremal limit. This infinite throat may suggest that the effective size of the black-hole system diverges in the extremal (zero-temperature) limit</subfield>
    <subfield code="9">refextract</subfield>
    <subfield code="o">5</subfield>
  </datafield>
